nvestments cut across the international public and private categories used elsewhere in this report though it is not possible to know the exact breakdown in the ASEAN region. This structure of Chinese investment matters when considering the role of Chinese policy toward investment in ASEAN and the rest of the world, and the influence of key Chinese policies on patterns of investment in the future.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "9abadbd2-007a-4528-ac2d-61030e42f0c7": {"__data__": {"id_": "9abadbd2-007a-4528-ac2d-61030e42f0c7", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asean-china-undp-financing-sustainable-development-goals-asean", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "ASEAN-China-UNDP Financing the Sustainable Development Goals in ASEAN", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asean-china-undp-financing-sustainable-development-goals-asean", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "758168a1682c65913c85dffc4f4bd45de982946ec32d71e27fd45d854a558670"}, "2": {"node_id": "b18cba6e-406c-4917-a621-0a4ad63e2ce7", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asean-china-undp-financing-sustainable-development-goals-asean", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "8f7886feecd3251680ab1bf2671d1318090d18466cdf2f71e9883e4d2e80bc79"}}, "hash": "f5434d93c072659300189c4b599386d5527392bdcf122980cd44d33121eb1977", "text": "S